🏨 Hostel Management System

A MERN stack application designed to simplify and automate hostel management operations for both admins and students.

✨ Features
🔐 Authentication
Login / Signup system with secure access
🧑‍💼 Admin Panel
Student registration
Attendance management
Complaint handling
Mess management
Invoice generation
Suggestion management
🎓 Student Panel
View attendance records
Request mess off
View invoices
Submit complaints
Send suggestions
⚙️ Tech Stack
MongoDB
Express.js
React.js
Node.js
Concurrently
📦 Installation

Install Node.js and MongoDB on your system.

Then clone the project and install dependencies:

cd client
npm install
cd ../server
npm install
cd ../
npm install -g concurrently
🗄️ Database Setup
Create a MongoDB database named:
hostel
Import required collections (example: users, complaints, invoices, etc.)
🚀 Run the Project
npm run dev
🔐 Environment Variables

Create a .env file inside the backend/server folder:

MONGO_URI=mongodb://127.0.0.1:27017/hostel
JWT_SECRET=Anappleadaykeepsthedoctoraway
